      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私はまだ子供ですけど、お二人のおかげでセンターも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I'm still a kid‚ thanks to you two‚ I've had the experience of",
        "id": ""
